back.description: The returned text of the area, if null returned, backArrow would not be rendered
back.description_zh: 返回的区域文本，如果返回 null，则不会呈现 backArrow

backArrow.description: Whether to display the arrow of the return area, you can also pass in ReactNode for customization
backArrow.description_zh: 是否显示返回区域的箭头，也可以传入 ReactNode 进行自定义

left.description: Content on the left, rendered on the right side of the return area
left.description_zh: 内容在左侧，呈现在返回区域的右侧

right.description: The content of the right side

events.name: onBack
events.description: Callback after clicking the return area
